{"tid":720324,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"梅拿笑巴西慘敗 丹迪﹕再講打鑊","createTime":"2018-06-28T00:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T00:06:41.000Z","uid":19552,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"cb9eadcdf0da53a27fa2fc1e3070c89aff3608eb","tid":720324,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:00:00.000Z","msg":"【明報專訊】巴西於世界盃4強大敗予德國1：7，事隔半年，睇怕都冇乜球迷記得，但效力拜仁慕尼黑的森巴後衛丹迪就日日生不如死，因為有個口臭隊友湯馬士梅拿，經常以這場歷史慘敗開玩笑，一直啞忍的丹迪終於忍唔住發火：「隊友可以開玩笑，但絕對不能關於這場比賽，當一個玩笑講出嚟冇人笑，即係唔好笑。湯馬士，你唔好再講，否則我每日操練都會一拳拳咁打你！」"},{"pid":"cd1811b92cdf794199726454ec761045f0ca197e","tid":720324,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  今次梅拿縮返去佢老母個閪都唔掂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ec1dd56516b38a8810d65a2968bdf1600b1b88","tid":720324,"uid":13375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:04:38.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"cf9622a3503d19cc385da69961962f6684a3bcb8","tid":720324,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:04:38.000Z","msg":"巴西真係慘<br />\n連報仇機會都冇"},{"pid":"0dfdcfe32f62cde15fd2a6a6ec15a2361b607a1e","tid":720324,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T00:06:41.000Z","msg":"拜仁親生仔你敢打？<br />\n唔怪得走埋"}]}